quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  76,1,"Has there [not] come upon man a period of time when he was not a thing [even] mentioned?"
  76,2,"Indeed, We created man from a sperm-drop mixture<sup foot_note=197665>1</sup> that We may try him; and We made him hearing and seeing.",footnotes:197665:1
  76,3,"Indeed, We guided him to the way, be he grateful or be he ungrateful."
  76,4,"Indeed, We have prepared for the disbelievers chains and shackles and a blaze."
  76,5,"Indeed, the righteous will drink from a cup [of wine] whose mixture is of Kāfūr,<sup foot_note=197666>1</sup>",footnotes:197666:1